Parse an RSS feed (XML)

Source: R/rss.R
rss_to_df.Rd

Parse an RSS feed (XML)

rss_to_df(rss_feed)

Arguments

rss_feed

A string pointing to the RSS URL.

Value

A tibble with RSS data.

Examples

rss_to_df("https://www.sciencegeist.ch/news/rss")
